reviews.text:
This recipe is fire. I mixed a sample, let it sit overnight, tried it in the morning... Haven't changed flavors yet, probably will finish the sample before I change flavors already mixed 30ml, and... likely I am going to be making a lot more. I can see this as a perfect morning vape for me. &#xD;
&#xD;
This tea has an amazing balance of bitterness, it really just absolutely nails it. It also juuuust lingers on your tongue after the exhale and then creates for this mouth feeling that is....... Just like you took a sip of tea. Just the lightest creaminess to it I guess from the shisha/marshmallow, nails it, and the sweet/tart/juiciness... It's just so accurate. &#xD;
&#xD;
FWIW, I never have tried the juice this inspired this recipe, but, I knew I had to try it from the great description here -- a well thought out and designed flavor, and worth picking up the exact flavors.
